#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.mode.mode_series:1 of
msgid ""
"Return the mode(s) of the Series. The mode is the value that appears most"
" often. There can be multiple modes. Always returns Series even if only "
"one value is returned. :param dropna: Don't consider counts of NaN/NaT. "
":type dropna: bool, default True"
msgstr ""
"返回 Series 的众数。众数是出现频率最高的值。可以有多个众数。即使只返回"
"一个值，也始终返回 Series。:param dropna: 不考虑 NaN/NaT 的计数。:type "
"dropna: bool，默认为 True"

#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.mode.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.mode.mode_series:7 of
msgid "Modes of the Series in sorted order."
msgstr "按排序顺序返回 Series 的众数。"

